data.description: Back on the market due to no fault of the seller. Don't let this beautiful property pass you by!   Location,location, location! Here is your chance to own your little piece of country heaven but still have access to the conveniences of living near town. This immaculate jewel sits on the edge of Peru and offers 5 spacious bedrooms, three walk-in closets, and 2 full baths.  This home is ideal for year-round entertaining as it offers two fireplaces; one on the main floor and one in the finished basement for winter parties as well as a spacious backyard for summer get togethers. The stunning kitchen offers a view across the landscaped front yard complete with brand new granite countertops and a tasteful tile backsplash. Multiple updates have been done to this property including updated wiring, plumbing, new furnace boiler, and privacy fencing.  In addition to the recent upgrades, particular care has been taken to keep this home exceptionally clean. You will be impressed with the level of detail given in the upgrades as well as the maintenance of this home.
